Alan Gifford https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alan_Gifford 0 Alan Gifford, born John Lennox, (March 11, 1911 – March 20, 1989) was an American-born actor from Taunton, Massachusetts, who worked mainly in Britain, where he died in Blairgowrie, Perthshire, Scotland aged 78.
